<bibRefCitation author="Hensley, D. A. &amp; Randall, J. E." box="[1058,1368,333,359]" pageId="25" pageNumber="180" pagination="1119 - 1126" refId="ref45207" refString="Hensley, D. A. &amp; Randall, J. E. (1993) Description of a new flatfish of the Indo-Pacific genus Crossorhombus (Teleostei: Bothidae), with comments on congeners. Copeia, 1993 (4), 1119 - 1126. https: // doi. org / 10.2307 / 1447092" type="journal article" year="1993">Hensley and Randall, 1993</bibRefCitation>
